{"word":"πολυώδυνος","slug":"πολυώδυνος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πολυώδυνος</b></el> <el>(πολυ-ώδῠνος, ον,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ὀδύνη'><el>ὀδύνη</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>very painful</i>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <i>suffering great pain</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}